featured_reviews.review_id:
This is not a wakf masjid, but a prayer facility made in the stilt parking of a CHSociety. Hence, it is small and quite crowded for Friday prayers and Eid prayers. At times 2 sittings are done.
It is very well maintained and the managing committee is doing an excellent job. During Ramadan Iftar, sehri, trawi are held and special lectures on important occasions.
Yes the IC Colony muslim community needs to find an alternate more spacious place to have a regular mosque as the community is growing and besides the present building may anytime go into redevelopment.
I thank Allah for providing us with this facility close to my house and hope we will be blessed with another mosque here soon for our future generations.
